headline: TerrAscend Corp. (TSNDF) Reports Q2 Loss, Beats Revenue Estimates
summary: TerrAscend Corp. (TSNDF) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -50.00% and +0.21%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
